&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for a commercially sharp, high-energy Category Manager who understands consumer goods markets and knows how to scale fast-growing businesses. Someone who brings structure to fast growth, builds strong teams, and turns momentum into revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You won’t just “manage” this category. You’ll build, scale and own it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Own&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and execute the growth strategy for Trading Cards&lt;/li&gt;
