&lt;li&gt;Turn data into action across pricing, supply, marketing, and performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Anticipate hype cycles, demand shifts, and market trends before they peak&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build structure in a fast-scaling environment&lt;/li&gt;
