&lt;li&gt;Proven experience managing and developing direct reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relentless commercial drive and entrepreneurial energy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ability to create structure while scaling fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Confidence influencing cross-functional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical instincts — you make decisions backed by data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort operating in a fast-paced, target-driven environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity for trading cards or collector culture is a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
