&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;The customer service department plays an essential role in Catawiki, as our customer service representatives ensure that our customers return to our platform on a regular basis and thereby directly help grow the business. The customer service department is also a crucial link between departments, closely working with Sales and our Experts as well as other departments to improve the overall Customer Experience. Through their close customer contact, CS brings valuable feedback on possibilities for improvements in our services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
